        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/17/24/22/1",
        "text": [
          "22 - هشام بن إبراهيم، العباسي، صاحب يونس. طعن عليه، والطعن - عندي - في مذهبه، لا في نفسه."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "22 – Hishām b. Ibrāhīm, al-ʿAbbāsī.  Companion of Yūnus.  He has been accused, and the accusation – according to me – is regarding his madhhab, not regarding himself."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
